Autocorrelation

beer2 <- window(ausbeer, 
                start = 1992,
                end = 2006-.1)
lag.plot(beer2, 
         lags = 9, 
         do.lines = FALSE)

This shows positive correlation every fourth season and some negative correlation with the second prior season.

Acf()

Acf(beer2)

This plot clearly shows the negative and positive correlations
